===========================================================
Build & Install:
===========================================================

cmakekde 

<copy scim-panel-dbus to your dir where scim-panel-gtk lives in>

===========================================================
Configure:
===========================================================
edit your scim's global config file,
 ( it's /etc/scim/global in my box(Archlinux distro). )
change this line:

/DefaultPanelProgram = scim-panel-gtk

into:

/DefaultPanelProgram = scim-panel-dbus

reboot your system (or manually kill all scim related process)

===========================================================
Run:
===========================================================
kimpanel (standalone app)
or 
add im panel Applet to your panel 

===========================================================
Uninstall:
===========================================================
goto source directory, 

make uninstall
rm <your dir where scim-panel-gtk lives in>/scim-panel-dbus

edit your scim's global config file,
 ( it's /etc/scim/global in my box(Archlinux distro). )
change this line:

/DefaultPanelProgram = scim-panel-dbus

back to:

/DefaultPanelProgram = scim-panel-gtk

then reboot your system (or manually kill all scim related process)
